data.description: New pics coming, owners have added tile throughout home except the bedrooms!!! New Fence coming soon!!Why wait for new construction to be built and then have them raise the sale price on you when home is almost finished. You can have a Beautiful home now and receive a 5k credit towards closing costs for all full price offers!! !!Walk into this Cozy home with 4 bedrooms and 2 baths. Room for everyone in the house. All doors are 5 panel doors and forget those accordion closet doors that fall off the rail in a few years. This home is built to last. With Dark cabinets and granite counter tops you will live in style. Recessed lighting through the home. Shutters to keep your family safe through a hurricane and pest control tubes built in the walls to keep the unwanted pest out. Must come see this home and make it yours today.
